  "description": {
   "en": "There was a young lady from an influential family that was famous for being a sloth. It was said that if she could lay down, she would not sit; and if she could sit, she would not stand.   \r\n  \r\nThere was a young master from an influential family who was educated, talented, and had unparalleled good looks. However, the best-among-men young master was rumored to have an unmentionable disease?! Yang Zhaojun only wished to become a chamber's sloth, but unfortunately for her, the Gods had other plans.  \r\n  \r\nWith a smile, she captivated the young master's heart. Would Zhaojun be willing to spend the rest of her life with him?"
  },
